1
00:00:58,960 --> 00:01:00,920
Have you found out which hospital

2
00:01:01,320 --> 00:01:03,120
Gu Haoran is hiding in right now?

3
00:01:03,320 --> 00:01:03,800
I have,

4
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:04,800
Young Master.

5
00:01:04,920 --> 00:01:05,680
Good.

6
00:01:07,280 --> 00:01:09,210
Tomorrow is Gu Haoran's birthday.

7
00:01:09,520 --> 00:01:10,560
I also want you

8
00:01:11,520 --> 00:01:13,440
to send him a big gift.

9
00:01:14,400 --> 00:01:15,200
Young Master,

10
00:01:15,200 --> 00:01:16,360
do you want me to...

11
00:01:17,880 --> 00:01:18,560
Exactly.

12
00:01:19,760 --> 00:01:21,220
I want to turn his birthday

13
00:01:22,080 --> 00:01:24,039
into the anniversary of his death.

14
00:01:25,320 --> 00:01:26,120
Young Master,

15
00:01:26,440 --> 00:01:28,280
you're making this too difficult for me.

16
00:01:28,280 --> 00:01:29,280
After all, this is

17
00:01:29,720 --> 00:01:30,760
too big.

18
00:01:31,280 --> 00:01:32,080
Don't worry.

19
00:01:33,920 --> 00:01:36,240
When I become the chairman of the group,

20
00:01:38,039 --> 00:01:39,770
the position of vice president

21
00:01:40,720 --> 00:01:42,120
will be yours.

22
00:01:46,640 --> 00:01:48,039
Thank you, Young Master.

23
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:49,200
Rest assured.

24
00:01:49,360 --> 00:01:51,479
Trust me. Han Chen won't let you down.

25
00:01:52,600 --> 00:01:53,240
And

26
00:01:54,440 --> 00:01:56,360
when sending Gu Haoran away,

27
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:59,520
take He Nan along too.

28
00:01:59,680 --> 00:02:00,120
Okay.

29
00:02:00,360 --> 00:02:00,880
Okay.

30
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:06,480
Director Han,

31
00:02:07,400 --> 00:02:08,520
Mr. Gu and Luo Xin

32
00:02:08,639 --> 00:02:10,100
haven't been seen lately.

33
00:02:10,720 --> 00:02:11,450
The chairman

34
00:02:11,480 --> 00:02:12,960
went abroad to discuss cooperation.

35
00:02:12,960 --> 00:02:13,640
And Luo Xin,

36
00:02:13,840 --> 00:02:15,920
she has been taking care of the second young master recently.

37
00:02:15,920 --> 00:02:16,480
Mr. Gu?

38
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:17,280
Yes.

39
00:02:17,440 --> 00:02:18,120
Is he awake?

40
00:02:18,560 --> 00:02:19,240
Not really.

41
00:02:19,760 --> 00:02:22,160
Just worried that something might happen.

42
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:22,960
Happen?

43
00:02:23,200 --> 00:02:24,460
What's wrong with him?

44
00:02:24,760 --> 00:02:25,680
A while ago,

45
00:02:25,880 --> 00:02:28,320
an unexpected guest broke into the hospital

46
00:02:28,320 --> 00:02:30,280
and almost killed the second young master.

47
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:31,880
Why didn't I know about this?

48
00:02:32,040 --> 00:02:33,720
The chairman asked to keep it a secret,

49
00:02:33,720 --> 00:02:35,160
so I didn't tell you.

50
00:02:37,680 --> 00:02:38,480
Director Han,

51
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:41,090
do you have time to take me to see Mr. Gu?

52
00:02:43,840 --> 00:02:45,000
Is tomorrow okay?

53
00:02:45,600 --> 00:02:48,560
Tomorrow happens to be the second young master's birthday.

54
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:48,960
Okay,

55
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:50,020
no problem.

56
00:02:50,760 --> 00:02:51,880
Okay. See you tomorrow.

57
00:02:51,880 --> 00:02:52,840
I'll leave you to your work.

58
00:02:52,840 --> 00:02:53,320
Okay.

59
00:03:06,040 --> 00:03:06,640
Chairman.

60
00:03:07,320 --> 00:03:09,240
I have settled Young Master Haoran down.

61
00:03:09,240 --> 00:03:10,770
Did you assign more people?

62
00:03:11,040 --> 00:03:11,920
As you ordered,

63
00:03:12,440 --> 00:03:14,040
I have doubled the manpower.

64
00:03:15,760 --> 00:03:16,400
Luo Xin,

65
00:03:16,760 --> 00:03:18,520
about Haoran's accident this time,

66
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:19,520
what do you think?

67
00:03:21,560 --> 00:03:22,400
I suspect

68
00:03:23,400 --> 00:03:25,130
it was done by an acquaintance.

69
00:03:26,600 --> 00:03:28,000
You also suspect He Nan?

70
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:28,680
No.

71
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:31,010
Mr. He has no motive for murder.

72
00:03:32,560 --> 00:03:35,760
Instead, the eldest young master is the most suspicious.

73
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:40,160
It seems

74
00:03:40,320 --> 00:03:42,320
we need to choose the best time

75
00:03:42,480 --> 00:03:43,760
to put on a good show

76
00:03:44,079 --> 00:03:46,600
and catch a rat in a trap.

77
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:49,940
Mr. He, please come in.

78
00:03:50,480 --> 00:03:50,920
Okay.

79
00:03:54,760 --> 00:03:55,690
Where is Luo Xin?

80
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:57,160
Didn't she come to take care of Mr. Gu?

81
00:03:57,160 --> 00:03:58,720
Secretary Luo probably went to get his medicine.

82
00:03:58,720 --> 00:03:59,640
She'll be right back.

83
00:03:59,640 --> 00:04:00,160
Mr. He,

84
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:01,920
please make yourself at home.

85
00:04:01,920 --> 00:04:02,400
Okay.

86
00:04:23,640 --> 00:04:24,160
Mr. Gu.

87
00:04:25,200 --> 00:04:26,840
I heard from Director Han yesterday

88
00:04:26,840 --> 00:04:28,170
that you were attacked.

89
00:04:28,840 --> 00:04:29,960
I was very worried about you,

90
00:04:29,960 --> 00:04:31,020
so I came to see you.

91
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:36,159
You definitely wouldn't have guessed it.

92
00:04:36,159 --> 00:04:37,420
Now I am also Gu Haoran.

93
00:04:38,880 --> 00:04:39,810
But don't worry.

94
00:04:40,280 --> 00:04:41,340
After you recover,

95
00:04:41,640 --> 00:04:42,840
I will leave on my own.

96
00:04:43,480 --> 00:04:45,340
You can continue being Gu Haoran,

97
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:47,210
and I'll continue being He Nan.

98
00:04:49,159 --> 00:04:49,690
Oh right,

99
00:04:51,200 --> 00:04:52,159
I've met Ziqing.

100
00:04:54,120 --> 00:04:55,380
She's a very nice girl.

101
00:04:56,480 --> 00:04:57,080
Later on,

102
00:04:58,400 --> 00:05:01,400
we are going to participate in the Longguo Grand Prix together.

103
00:05:01,400 --> 00:05:03,060
I hope you will be awake by then

104
00:05:03,880 --> 00:05:06,410
and can witness us winning the championship.

105
00:05:19,760 --> 00:05:20,520
Gasoline.

106
00:05:25,520 --> 00:05:26,320
Director Han.

107
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:28,680
Han Chen.

108
00:05:29,040 --> 00:05:30,040
You despicable person,

109
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:31,100
this is a hospital!

110
00:05:31,280 --> 00:05:31,760
He Nan,

111
00:05:32,159 --> 00:05:33,880
go to hell together with the Second Young Master!

112
00:05:33,880 --> 00:05:34,409
Han Chen.

113
00:05:34,760 --> 00:05:36,090
You despicable coward.

114
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:37,240
Open it.

115
00:05:37,680 --> 00:05:38,120
He Nan.

116
00:05:38,320 --> 00:05:39,320
You can't escape.

117
00:05:39,760 --> 00:05:40,690
Just wait to die.

118
00:05:41,240 --> 00:05:42,300
This is a hospital.

119
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:50,080
Han Chen.

120
00:05:53,200 --> 00:05:53,960
Open the door.

121
00:05:53,960 --> 00:05:54,760
Open the door.

122
00:06:06,080 --> 00:06:06,740
Who are you?

123
00:06:09,880 --> 00:06:10,600
Gu Haoran.

124
00:06:13,080 --> 00:06:13,680
It's you.

125
00:06:18,600 --> 00:06:19,240
Stop.

126
00:06:20,760 --> 00:06:21,520
Chairman.

127
00:06:22,120 --> 00:06:22,680
Han Chen.

128
00:06:23,080 --> 00:06:24,360
How dare you.

129
00:06:25,640 --> 00:06:26,320
Haotian.

130
00:06:27,000 --> 00:06:28,530
I'm so disappointed in you.

131
00:06:29,360 --> 00:06:30,890
Out of a moment of jealousy,

132
00:06:31,160 --> 00:06:33,620
you actually tried to kill your own brother.

133
00:06:34,440 --> 00:06:35,040
Grandpa.

134
00:06:35,880 --> 00:06:36,940
Since we were kids,

135
00:06:37,400 --> 00:06:39,320
I've been better than him in every way,

136
00:06:39,320 --> 00:06:40,850
but you always favored him.

137
00:06:41,280 --> 00:06:41,880
Why?

138
00:06:42,440 --> 00:06:43,770
I am also your grandson.

139
00:06:44,120 --> 00:06:45,400
How am I worse than him?

140
00:06:49,200 --> 00:06:51,930
You think you are better than Haoran in every way.

141
00:06:52,040 --> 00:06:52,880
It's a pity,

142
00:06:53,680 --> 00:06:55,409
that your character is flawed.

143
00:06:59,400 --> 00:07:00,360
Character?

144
00:07:01,280 --> 00:07:02,480
In this world,

145
00:07:03,560 --> 00:07:05,200
if you want to have everything,

146
00:07:05,200 --> 00:07:07,060
you must use any means necessary.

147
00:07:07,120 --> 00:07:08,120
Everything I did

148
00:07:08,600 --> 00:07:10,120
was for our Gu Group.

149
00:07:11,520 --> 00:07:13,320
Since you chose to play dirty,

150
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:16,330
you should be ready to accept your defeat.

151
00:07:16,560 --> 00:07:18,420
Winners take all and losers fall.

152
00:07:18,440 --> 00:07:19,900
You must understand that.

153
00:07:21,560 --> 00:07:21,920
I...

154
00:07:22,000 --> 00:07:22,530
Someone!

155
00:07:23,200 --> 00:07:25,260
Take them both to the police station.

156
00:07:33,720 --> 00:07:34,520
Gu Haoran.

157
00:07:35,520 --> 00:07:36,800
When I get out,

158
00:07:37,240 --> 00:07:38,200
you are dead.

159
00:07:39,280 --> 00:07:39,940
Gu Haotian,

160
00:07:41,080 --> 00:07:42,280
your mind is corrupt.

161
00:07:42,360 --> 00:07:44,420
In the end, it will all be for nothing.

162
00:07:58,840 --> 00:07:59,500
Old Master.

163
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:01,120
I suspect

164
00:08:01,840 --> 00:08:04,040
Haoran's car crash wasn't an accident.

165
00:08:04,960 --> 00:08:05,890
What do you mean?

166
00:08:06,800 --> 00:08:08,480
I always feel that in this conspiracy,

167
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:09,360
whether it's me,

168
00:08:09,360 --> 00:08:09,890
Ding Wen,

169
00:08:10,120 --> 00:08:10,920
or Gu Haotian,

170
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:12,440
we are all just pawns.

171
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:14,240
The real mastermind

172
00:08:14,240 --> 00:08:15,770
is still behind the scenes.

173
00:08:17,480 --> 00:08:18,440
Makes sense.

174
00:08:19,440 --> 00:08:21,840
The Dragon Country Grand Prix is coming up.

175
00:08:21,880 --> 00:08:23,160
They will show

176
00:08:23,360 --> 00:08:24,690
their true colors soon.

177
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:27,640
Zixi,

178
00:08:28,680 --> 00:08:30,340
I will definitely avenge you.

179
00:08:32,360 --> 00:08:33,039
This race

180
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:34,559
for both the cars and the drivers

181
00:08:34,559 --> 00:08:36,000
is a very severe test.

182
00:08:36,320 --> 00:08:37,679
Since it's a team relay race,

183
00:08:37,679 --> 00:08:39,640
the coordination between drivers

184
00:08:39,760 --> 00:08:41,220
must be extremely strict.

185
00:08:41,280 --> 00:08:41,760
Since

186
00:08:41,799 --> 00:08:43,320
our teamwork is not good enough yet,

187
00:08:43,320 --> 00:08:44,560
we need to hurry up

188
00:08:44,920 --> 00:08:45,780
and train hard.

189
00:08:47,440 --> 00:08:48,120
Sometimes,

190
00:08:48,520 --> 00:08:49,520
to win as a team,

191
00:08:49,680 --> 00:08:51,610
you can sacrifice personal glory.

192
00:08:51,640 --> 00:08:52,170
Jingchi,

193
00:08:52,640 --> 00:08:54,770
I'm confident in your driving skills.

194
00:08:55,760 --> 00:08:56,360
As for

195
00:08:57,280 --> 00:08:57,760
Ziqing,

196
00:08:59,000 --> 00:09:01,060
we need to give you hellish training.

197
00:09:02,680 --> 00:09:03,200
Okay.

198
00:09:04,800 --> 00:09:05,200
Okay,

199
00:09:05,920 --> 00:09:06,580
get to work.

200
00:09:16,320 --> 00:09:17,040
Mr. He Nan,

201
00:09:17,280 --> 00:09:18,010
I have Zixi's

202
00:09:18,120 --> 00:09:19,080
secret files on the Racing Alliance.

203
00:09:19,080 --> 00:09:19,760
Who are you?

204
00:09:19,960 --> 00:09:21,760
Under Likun Overpass at 10:00 tonight.

205
00:09:21,760 --> 00:09:22,000
Come quickly.

206
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:24,440
Hello, the number you dialed is powered off.
